snippet.textDisplay: I love this song so much. Not because of how good it is, but because of the instruments that they put into it. I felt like the past 2 albums were all electronic. Like no physical instruments, just keyboard and online sounds. And that may not be true, but that’s just what it felt personally to me. But in this song, I could hear a real guitar, real drums, and a real bass being played, and I missed that. Keep it up Gorillaz 🙌
